name: LOVE & SPACETIME
description: This is a variant of a previous work from June 3rd, 2020. I love this one so much that I wanted to see if altering the colors and lightening the tone could create a different emotional look and feel to it. The pastels and almost invisible qualities imbue a sense of ethereal temporality. Our lives are temporal moments of consciousness strung together like pearls on a string. I wanted to emphasize that feeling. The variant works just as good as the first and yet completely different.
